    <item>
      <title>特鲁多称特朗普通话后推迟 30 天征收关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trudeau-says-trump-tariffs-delayed-30-days-after-call</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多周一宣布，在与唐纳德·特朗普总统通话 30 天后，将暂停征收新的美国关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trudeau-says-trump-tariffs-delayed-30-days-after-call</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 21:42:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥告诉国会，美国国际开发署可能在审查后被废除</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/rubio-tells-congress-that-usaid-may-be-abolished-after-review</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻看到的一封信显示，美国国务卿马尔科·卢比奥向国会表示，一旦他的团队完成对美国国际开发署实践的审查，该署可能会被并入国务院，并作为一个独立机构废除。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/rubio-tells-congress-that-usaid-may-be-abolished-after-review</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 21:14:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命的华盛顿特区律师提出保护马斯克的 DOGE 员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-appointed-dc-attorney-offers-to-protect-musk-s-doge-staff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国哥伦比亚特区新任临时检察官表示，他将对任何妨碍或威胁伊隆·马斯克政府效率团队的人采取法律行动，在该团队与美国各机构公务员多次发生冲突之后，这一举措的风险进一步上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-appointed-dc-attorney-offers-to-protect-musk-s-doge-staff</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 20:54:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>叙利亚总统透露与美国支持的组织进行会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/syria-s-president-reveals-talks-with-us-backed-group-over-arms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[叙利亚当局正在与美国支持的武装组织举行会谈，以控制这个饱受战争蹂躏的国家的火力，此举将在独裁者巴沙尔·阿萨德倒台后巩固新统治者的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/syria-s-president-reveals-talks-with-us-backed-group-over-arms</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 20:42:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前总统乔·拜登与人才经纪公司 CAA 签约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/former-president-joe-biden-signs-with-talent-agency-caa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统乔·拜登与创新艺术家经纪公司重新签约，回到担任副总统八年后管理他的人才代表身边。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/former-president-joe-biden-signs-with-talent-agency-caa</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 19:54:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普希望乌克兰保证获得稀土用于战争援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-wants-ukraine-to-guarantee-rare-earths-access-for-war-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他的政府希望与乌克兰达成一项协议，让这个饱受战争蹂躏的国家获得其稀土资源，以换取其帮助其防御俄罗斯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-wants-ukraine-to-guarantee-rare-earths-access-for-war-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 19:30:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克在债务违约风险辩论中采取的举措</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/musk-s-moves-on-treasury-risks-a-debate-over-us-payments-default</link>
      <description><![CDATA[除美国财政部在等待国会提高债务上限的同时现金储备减少的情况外，债券市场参与者通常不会过多关注该部门的支付处理部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/musk-s-moves-on-treasury-risks-a-debate-over-us-payments-default</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 18:35:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称马斯克无法独自阻止国库支付</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-says-musk-sees-treasury-payments-but-can-t-stop-them-alone</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，埃隆·马斯克可以访问财政部系统，这使他能够在付款前监控联邦支出，但这位世界首富无权在未经批准的情况下自行停止付款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-says-musk-sees-treasury-payments-but-can-t-stop-them-alone</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 18:26:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥称美国国际开发署需要接管以实现外交政策目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/rubio-says-he-s-now-in-charge-of-usaid-as-relief-agency-teeters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国务卿马尔科·卢比奥表示，他目前负责美国国际开发署，他表示此举对于使其与美国的外交政策目标保持一致是必要的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/rubio-says-he-s-now-in-charge-of-usaid-as-relief-agency-teeters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 17:33:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
